  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgentListImp
    AgentListImp class manages a list of agents.

    MAPDDLParserImp class implements a MAPDDL parser.

    ParserImp class implements a native FMAP-PDDL parser.
    SynAnalyzer
    Syntactic analyzer for the native PDDL-FMAP Language.
    SynAnalyzer.Token
    Syntactic tokens.
    TaskImp
    Implementation of an ungrounded planning task.
    TaskTypes
    TaskTypes class contains several types for ungrounded task elements.
    TaskTypes.ConditionImp
    ConditionImp class represents an ungrounded condition.
    TaskTypes.FactImp
    FactImp class reprenets ungrounded facts.
    TaskTypes.FunctionImp
    FunctionImp class represents ungrounded functions.
    TaskTypes.NumericEffectImp
    NumericEffectImp class implements action numeric effects.
    TaskTypes.NumericExpressionImp
    NumericExpressionImp class implements a numeric expression.
    TaskTypes.OperatorImp
    OperatorImp class implements operators (ungrounded actions).
    TaskTypes.ParameterImp
    A parameter represents a name with a list of types.
    TaskTypes.SharedDataImp
    SharedDataImp class represents shared data, i.e. public information that the current agent can share with other agents.
